# Internationalization Implementation

## Implementation Details
- Use next-intl for UI translations
- Implement locale routing: `/pt/activities`, `/en/activities`
- Store translations in `messages/` directory
- Use proper locale detection

## Locale Detection
1. URL path (`/pt/activities`)
2. Accept-Language header
3. Default to Portuguese

## Content Structure
- Store multilingual content in JSONB format
- Use locale keys: `{ "pt": "texto", "en": "text" }`
- Default locale is Portuguese (pt)
- Fallback to English (en) when translation missing

## Accessibility Support
- Support RTL languages if needed
- Use proper locale formatting
- Implement proper date/time handling
- Consider cultural differences
